The <ansi fg="command">bank</ansi> command lets you deposit and withdraw from a bank. 

<ansi fg="yellow">Usage: </ansi>

  <ansi fg="command">bank</ansi> - See your gold on hand and in the bank

  <ansi fg="command">deposit [amount/all]</ansi> - Deposit an amount of gold (or all) into the bank
  
  <ansi fg="command">withdraw [amount/all]</ansi> - Withdraw an amount of gold (or all) from the bank

